verbose_text: In addition in this study we found that among cases with positive VEGF expression in portal structures, 50.0% of them had marked bridging fibrosis, and only one case (3.1%) of them had absent or portal expansion of some portal tracts, while among those with negative VEGF in portal structures, 39.0% of them had absent or portal expansion of some portal tracts and only 9.8% had marked bridging fibrosis (p < 0.001).
